    "将清空全部记分流水与兑换记录，总分归零；规则与奖励目录保留。此操作不可撤销。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "This clears all score activity and redemptions and resets the total to zero. Rules and rewards are kept. This can't be undone."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "将清空全部记录、恢复默认规则与奖励、积分归零。此操作不可撤销。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "This clears all records, restores the default rules and rewards, and resets points to zero. This can't be undone."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "将用最近一次备份覆盖当前数据。": {
